title: Classic Rewind of Lil Duval Interview and Ask Yee
itunes:title: Classic Rewind of Lil Duval Interview and Ask Yee
description:
Today on the show we rewinded back to when we had the Wallstreet Trapper stop by and speak on the importance of stocks and how he as introduced to it. Also, we flashed back to the last time Lil Duval was in the building, and tried not to start any trouble but of course caused some controversy with some of his comments about 30 year olds having roommates, which we ended up making a topic out of. Also, we flashed back to some of the best advice Yee and C and E gave to listeners. And Lasty remember when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to coach Hubert Davis for his comments on having a white wife? check it out.
